Package: drbd-reactor
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libssl3t64
Description: DRBD resource agent and monitoring daemon
 drbd-reactor is a daemon that reacts to DRBD cluster events and executes
 configured reactions such as promoting resources, adjusting quorum, and
 integrating with Pacemaker or other cluster managers.
